    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but if we're looking at the math for hitting net zero by 2050, isn't it basically impossible to do it with just wind and solar? it seems like nuclear is pretty much a necessity at this point for any realistic plan.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
